I have to agree with all the reviews. I went in for a me pair of running shoes after being out of running for years. They checked out my gait and then came out with like 8 boxes of shoes. He sat down with me and helped me narrow it down to 2. I then took them outside and finally settled on a pair. These guys really take the time, take off the pressure and the prices are reasonable.

